# Build-time injected by scripts/inject-build-config.mjs. Never commit —
# typecheck/start/build always re-inject before tsc runs, so a fresh
# clone runs through `npm run typecheck` cleanly because the script
# writes the file first. Production builds bake the bearer secret into
# this file, which is a second reason to keep it out of git.
